                            <comment id="13157670" author="psteitz" created="Sun, 27 Nov 2011 06:01:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I can&apos;t seem to make this fail and I have added tests that would indicate that array segments are being handled properly.  Can you provide an example showing a failure?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13158395" author="tn" created="Mon, 28 Nov 2011 12:51:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have found a small bug wrt this bug report. The sum of the weights is calculated on the whole weight array rather than the specified sub-array [begin, begin + length).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See the attached patch for more details. Still need a testcase to verify that it finally addresses the original bug report.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13159855" author="psteitz" created="Wed, 30 Nov 2011 06:25:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Good catch, Thomas.  Thanks!  Patch, with test case added, committed in r1208291.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
